<html>
<head>
  <style>
    code {
      font-family: "Nimbus Mono L", "Monospace", monospace;
      color: #00843E;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    h3 {
      color: #00843E;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<h3>Updating SAP HANA software</h3>
<p>
  Please update SAP HANA software on node <b><code><%= node.name %></code></b>
  (site <code><%= node.site %></code>) using your preferred update method.
</p>
<% if model.nfs.should_mount? %>
    <p>
      <i>Note:</i> The NFS share <code><%= model.nfs.source %></code> was mounted to
      <code><%= model.nfs.mount_path %></code>.
    </p>
<% end %>
<% if model.nfs.copy_medium? %>
    <p>
      <i>Note:</i> The contents of the NFS share have been copied locally to
      <code><%= model.nfs.copy_path %></code>.
    </p>
<% end %>
<% if part == :remote %>
<p></p>
<p>Please use the <code>--hdbupd_server_nostart</code> option for the HDB LCM.
Refer to the "How To Perform System Replication for SAP HANA" guide for further instructions.</p>
<% end %>
<p></p>
<p>Click "Next" once the site <code><%= node.site %></code> is updated.</p>
</body>
</html>
